; ForgeOS FIRST-LAYER COMPARE (PA-style multi-panel)
; line_w=0.44 first_h=0.28 speed=12mm/s
; COLS spacing_ratio (L→R): 0.92 | 0.96 | 1.00 | 1.04
; ROWS first_flow (B→T): 0.96 | 1.00 | 1.04
; Pick flattest panel: side-by-side beads, no pile ridges, no gaps
; Legend strips: short single-line row under each col = spacing only @ flow 1.00

